FT  12 MAR 94 / UK Company News: Birkby wins 92% of In Shops
The recommended offer by Birkby for In Shops, a listed retail space
management company, has been accepted in respect of about 92 per cent of the
ordinary equity.
Valid acceptances received totalled 47.13m shares. The figure included 9.98m
shares which were the subject of irrevocable undertakings to accept the
offer.
The offer has been declared unconditional in all respects and remains open
for acceptance until further notice.
